  <h2 id="privacy-heading">1. Who We Are</h2>
  <p>Facware ("we", "our", or "us") is a custom software and systems integration company based in Chihuahua, Mexico, serving mid-market businesses in Mexico and the US Southwest. Our website is <a href="https://facware.com">https://facware.com</a> and our primary contact channel is <a href="/contact.html#contact-form">https://facware.com/contact.html</a>.</p>
  <p>This Privacy Policy applies to all personal information we collect through our website, email communications, and any other interactions you have with us.</p>

